          <p class='first-para'>
            It is not in the power of the Deputy Speaker to determine who turns up for a debate and decides to take part. It is up to us to turn up if we wish to take part.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0357P0_20001122_WH_10'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-anthony-steen' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
