          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0357P0_20001122_WH_12'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/sir-alan-haselhurst' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0357P0_20001122_WH_12' title='Link to this speech by Sir Alan Haselhurst' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
