      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0357P0_20001122_WH_38'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mrs-marion-roe' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0357P0_20001122_WH_38' title='Link to this speech by Mrs Marion Roe' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mrs-marion-roe" title="Mrs Marion Roe">Mrs. Marion Roe (in the Chair)</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            Order. I remind hon. Members that the House has decided that members of the Chairmen's Panel who take the Chair in Westminster Hall should be addressed by name. I should be addressed as Mrs. Roe.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
